title.narrative: Remittances Transparency - Empowering Remitters to Choose

description.narrative: This activity focuses on addressing challenges facing remitters when engaging with the remittances market. These challenges include information asymmetries about the prices charged by different remittance providers, and a lack of trust in different remittances products (particularly online-only products).
